      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="feature-title">Fund Wallet</div>
        <div class="feature-desc">Built-in USDT TRC20 crypto wallet. Deposit and withdraw with zero fees — automatic and instant 24/7.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <div class="feature-icon fi-red">
        <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#ff5252" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
      </div>
